        "rich_text_mEE3FU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "4. Property or Real Estate – A Long-Term Investment for Financial Growth",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>4. Property or Real Estate – A Long-Term Investment for Financial Growth</h2><p>Akshaya Tritiya is believed to be an ideal day for making major investments, especially in property or real estate. Buying land, a house, or starting the process of purchasing a property on this day is considered extremely fortunate.</p><p>Property investments symbolize stability, long-term growth, and financial security, which is why many families align these important decisions with auspicious occasions like Akshaya Tritiya.</p>",
