        "rich_text_pXQg9A": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "6. Vehicles – A Symbol of Progress and New Beginnings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>6. Vehicles – A Symbol of Progress and New Beginnings</h2><p>Buying a new vehicle on Akshaya Tritiya is believed to bring success, protection, and smooth journeys ahead. Many people choose this auspicious day to purchase a car, bike, or even commercial vehicles.</p><p>Since the festival symbolizes new beginnings, purchasing a vehicle on this day represents progress, growth, and moving forward in life.</p>",
