        "rich_text_fq6X6x": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "7. Home Essentials or Appliances – Bringing Positive Energy into Your Home",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>7. Home Essentials or Appliances – Bringing Positive Energy into Your Home</h2><p>Many households celebrate Akshaya Tritiya by purchasing home essentials or appliances. Buying items such as kitchen appliances, furniture, or home décor is believed to bring comfort and prosperity to the household.</p><p>These purchases symbolize improving your living space and welcoming positive energy into the home.</p>",
            "custom_id": "home",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_fCAGGi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "8. Financial Investments – A Modern Way to Grow Wealth",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>8. Financial Investments – A Modern Way to Grow Wealth</h2><p>In recent years, people have started celebrating Akshaya Tritiya by making financial investments. Buying stocks, mutual funds, or starting a new savings plan is seen as a modern way to attract long-term wealth.</p><p>The belief is that investments made on this day will grow steadily over time, reflecting the meaning of “Akshaya” — something that never diminishes.</p>",
            "custom_id": "financial",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_XDYJGC": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "9. Religious Idols or Spiritual Items – Inviting Divine Blessings into Your Home",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>9. Religious Idols or Spiritual Items – Inviting Divine Blessings into Your Home</h2><p>Many families bring home idols of Goddess Lakshmi or Lord Ganesha during Akshaya Tritiya. These idols are placed in home temples and worshipped during prayers.</p><p>Other spiritual purchases include brass lamps, puja thalis, or sacred symbols that represent peace, prosperity, and positive energy.</p>",
            "custom_id": "religious",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_rXW3ED": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "10. Business Tools or Work Equipment – A Step Toward Professional Growth",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>10. Business Tools or Work Equipment – A Step Toward Professional Growth</h2><p>Akshaya Tritiya is also considered a favorable time to start new business ventures or invest in professional growth. Entrepreneurs often purchase tools, machinery, or office equipment on this day.</p><p>These purchases symbolize expansion, productivity, and long-term success in business.</p>",
            "custom_id": "business",
